OL,3,CIconic building La Gondola could be
OL,4,Cdemolished after huge fire
OL,6,FAn iconic building in Derby could be
OL,7,Fdemolished after a fire broke out at
OL,8,Fthe site which was previously home to
OL,9,Fthe La Gondola restaurant.
OL,11,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,12,Fpremises on Osmaston Road near the
OL,13,Fcity centre at around 7pm on Sunday.
OL,14,FEight pumps and 45 firefighters were
OL,15,Fsent to tackle the blaze.
OL,17,FThe fire service has said
OL,18,Finvestigations are ongoing and the
OL,19,Fbuilding - which has been derelict for
OL,20,Fmore than a decade - is unlikely to be
OL,21,Fsaved.
