OL,3,CIconic building La Gondola could be
OL,4,Cdemolished after huge fire
OL,6,FResidents were told to keep their
OL,7,Fwindows and doors closed after a large
OL,8,Ffire broke out at the old La Gondola
OL,9,Fbuilding.
OL,11,FThe Osmaston Road venue has been empty
OL,12,Ffor more than a decade since it closed
OL,13,Fin 2009, but it was once a popular
OL,14,Fattraction in the city centre.
OL,16,FThe venue was probably best known for
OL,17,Fbeing visited by Gordon Ramsey in 2006
OL,18,Fas part of his Kitchen Nightmares
OL,19,Fseries.
