OL,3,CIconic building La Gondola could be
OL,4,Cdemolished after huge fire
OL,6,FThe Derbyshire Fire and Rescue Service
OL,7,Fshared an update shortly before 9pm
OL,8,Flast night, stating: "We are currently
OL,9,Fin attendance at a large fire on
OL,10,FOsmaston Road in Derby City Centre.
OL,12,F"We advise that local residents please
OL,13,Fkeep their windows and doors closed.
OL,14,FWe will keep you updated."
OL,16,FAn update from the service was then
OL,17,Fshared shortly after 7am on Monday.
