OL,3,CIconic building La Gondola could be
OL,4,Cdemolished after huge fire
OL,6,FIt stated: "Firefighters have worked
OL,7,Fthrough the night at the scene of a
OL,8,Ffire in a derelict building on
OL,9,FOsmaston Road Derby.
OL,11,F"Two fire engines and an aerial ladder
OL,12,Fplatform remain on scene this morning
OL,13,Fcontinuing to extinguish the fire. If
OL,14,Fyou can see or smell smoke, keep
OL,15,Fwindows and doors closed."
