OL,3,CIconic building La Gondola could be
OL,4,Cdemolished after huge fire
OL,6,FA new update from the fire service at
OL,7,F11.15am confirmed that firefighters
OL,8,Ffrom Ascot Drive Fire Station remain
OL,9,Fat the scene with the aerial ladder
OL,10,Fplatform. They are working to dampen
OL,11,Fdown the site and check for hotspots.
OL,13,FIn 2023 it was reported that the
OL,14,Fbuilding would be demolished after
OL,15,FDerby City Council's planning
OL,16,Fcommittee rejected plans for 42 new
OL,17,Fflats on the site. This was despite
OL,18,Fthe plans being recommended for
OL,19,Fapproval.
